Tasks:
    html            Alias for release:html

    release         Alias for release:html

    clean           Perform clean:app, clean:assets, clean:cache and clean:build tasks

    build:html      Create HTML build of an app. Concatenate all files specified in the
                    `package.json`, copy all assets and generate `index.html` file

    release:html    Create HTML build of an app. Concatenate and uglify all files
                    specified in the `package.json`, copy all assets and generate
                    `index.html` file

    clean:app       Remove app file from build destination

    clean:assets    Remove all assets from build destination

    clean:cache     Clean engine cache from all engine versions previously saved

    clean:build     Remove build folder

Options:
    --engine        Specify engine version that comes from Solpeo CDN or custom local / URL
                    path to the engine file

                    Default: <%=DEFAULT_ENGINE%>

    --no-cache      Don\t cache engine file specified by the --engine flag

                    Default: <%=DEFAULT_NO_CACHE%>

    --dest          Specify destination folder for a build

                    Default: <%=dest%>
